SEARCH
Package gw.api.modules.rest.framework.v1.inclusions

Interface InclusionMap<R extends RestElementResource>

Type Parameters:
R - The resource element type
public interface InclusionMap<R extends RestElementResource>
This class represents a map of keys, which represent the names of included resources that can be requested via the "include" query parameter, to callbacks that can be used to materialize the appropriate included resource upon request.
